:: Public Holidays
"Año Nuevo"				                 public on january 1
"Día de la ciudadanía americana"         public on march 2
"Día de la abolición de la esclavitud"   public on march 22
"Día de la constitución de Puerto Rico"  public on july 25
"Natalicio de José Celso Barbosa"        public on july 27
"Día de la Puertorriqueñidad"            public on november 19

:: Federal Holidays
"Natalicio de Martin Luther King"                                           public on third monday in january
"Día de los presidentes y las mujeres y hombres procéres de Puerto Rico"    public on third monday in february
"Día de la conmemoración de los muertos en la guerra"                       public on last monday in may
"Juneteenth"                                                                public on june 19
"Juneteenth"                                                                public on (([june 19] == [saturday after ([june 19])]) ?
                                                                                                     [friday before ([june 19])] : noop)
"Juneteenth"                                                                public on (([june 19] == [sunday   after ([june 19])]) ?
                                                                                                     [monday after  ([june 19])] : noop)
"Día de la independencia de los Estados Unidos"                             public on july 4
"Día del trabajo"                                                           public on first monday in september
"Día de la raza"                                                            public on second monday in october
"Día del veterano"                                                          public on november 11
"Día de acción de gracias"                                                  public on fourth thursday in november

:: Cultural
"Natalicio de Eugenio María de Hostos" cultural on january 11
"Día de San Valentín"	               cultural on february 14
"Natalicio de Luis Muñoz Marín"        cultural on february 18
"Natalicio de José de Diego"           cultural on april 16
"Día de las Madres"                    cultural on second sunday in may
"Día de los Padres"			           cultural on third sunday in june
"Noche de brujas"                      cultural on october 31
"Vispera de año nuevo"                 cultural on december 31

:: Religious
"Día de Reyes"                      public religious school on january 6
"Miércoles de ceniza"               religious on easter minus 46 days
"Domingo de Ramos"                  religious on easter minus 7 days
"Jueves Santo"                      religious on easter minus 3 days
"Viernes Santo"                     public religious on easter minus 2 days
"Sábado de Gloria"                  religious on easter minus 1 days
"Domingo de Pascua"                 religious on easter               
"Noche buena"		                religious cultural on december 24
"Navidad"                           public religious on december 25

:: School
"Grito de Lares"                    school on september 23

